name: MPMovieErrorLogEvent
desc: A single piece of information for a movie error log.

items.name: var date: Date!
items.desc: The date and time when the error occurred.

items.name: var uri: String!
items.desc: The URI of the item being played when the error occurred.

items.name: var serverAddress: String!
items.desc: The IP address of the web server that was the source of the error.

items.name: var playbackSessionID: String!
items.desc: A GUID (globally unique identifier) for the playback session.

items.name: var errorDomain: String!
items.desc: The network domain of the error.
